shape: sequence_diagram

relayer: Relayer
sui: Sui OApp
lz: LayerZero DVN
evm: EVM\nBosphorAdapter

relayer -> sui: execute_store(blob, intentId)
sui -> sui: Verify blob certification,\ncheck deadline,\nemit StorageExecuted
relayer -> sui: lz_send_proof(intentId, blobId, endEpoch)
sui -> lz: PTB via LZ endpoint\n(type 1 message)
lz -> lz: DVN verification
lz -> evm: _lzReceive()
evm -> evm: Decode proof,\nmark intent executed,\nemit IntentExecuted
